        <p class="saye-footer__brand-desc">Online canlı yoga ve meditasyon dersleri</p>
        <div class="saye-footer__contact">
          <a class="saye-footer__contact-link" href="mailto:info@sayeyoga.com">📧 info@sayeyoga.com</a>
          <a class="saye-footer__contact-link" href="/pages/iletisim">📷 @sayeyoga</a>
